- [Customization quickstart](https://spreecommerce.org/docs/developer/dashboard/customization/quickstart) — the registries this plugin uses
- [Plugin overview](https://spreecommerce.org/docs/developer/dashboard/plugins/overview) — packaging + publishing your plugin to npm
